                    materials inspired by nature and the northern climate. Above all, it made functionality and
                    durability the basis for good design.&nbsp;<span>With special attention to sustainable practices, we continue to build on the Nordic tradition of functional beauty and the mission to enhance life through well-designed everyday things. Our collections are carefully made to leave a lighter footprint and intended to be used and loved for a long time.</span>
